OL,3,CTwo-day-old pavement in Farnham to be
OL,4,Creplaced after crumbling away
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News Meridian's Harry Acton
OL,7,Freports from Farnham.
OL,9,FA freshly tarmacked street in Farnham
OL,10,Fis to be resurfaced, after it began to
OL,11,Fcrumble away.
OL,13,FWorks on White Cottage Close in the
OL,14,FSurrey town took place earlier this
OL,15,Fweek, as part of efforts to prolong
OL,16,Fthe life of the pavements.
OL,18,FHowever, once the work was completed,
OL,19,Fthe surface began to disintegrate.
