OL,3,CTwo-day-old pavement in Farnham to be
OL,4,Creplaced after crumbling away
OL,6,FSurrey County Council has acknowledged
OL,7,Fthat the works did not go to plan, and
OL,8,Fsays contractors will return next week
OL,9,F- weather permitting - to rectify the
OL,10,Fissues.
OL,12,FBut residents worry about their safety
OL,13,Fwhilst walking along the pavements, as
OL,14,Fholes have begun to form in several
OL,15,Fareas.
OL,17,FSamantha Higgins, who lives on the
OL,18,Fstreet with her husband and two young
OL,19,Fchildren, told ITV News Meridian that
OL,20,Fthe works were 'not good enough'.
