OL,3,CTwo-day-old pavement in Farnham to be
OL,4,Creplaced after crumbling away
OL,6,FShe worries about her toddler walking
OL,7,Falong the pavement, as he could trip
OL,8,Fon some of tarmac that has lifted away.
OL,10,F"As a mother I've got two young
OL,11,Fchildren and we walk along the
OL,12,Fpavement every day", she said.
OL,14,F"I have to be very careful with my
OL,15,Ftoddler as he very unsteady on his
OL,16,Ffeet, and this is something he might
OL,17,Ftrip on.
OL,19,F"And of course I need to watch out for
OL,20,Fmy daughter as well. So it's just not
OL,21,Fgood enough.
