OL,6,F"It's also been completely ruined
OL,7,Foutside our property as well, and it
OL,8,Fdoesn't look very nice."
OL,10,FA Surrey County Council spokesperson
OL,11,Ftold ITV Meridian: "Repairs were
OL,12,Frecently made to the pavement on White
OL,13,FCottage Close, Farnham, using a cold
OL,14,Fsurface treatment which is an industry
OL,15,Fstandard practice to extend the life
OL,16,Fof the pavement.
OL,18,F"Unfortunately, the material hasn't
OL,19,Fdried and settled as it normally would.
